						As soon as she had finished saying this, she again made reverence, and
						sprung cheerfully into her throne, after which the trumpets began to sound
						again, which yet was not forceful enough to take the grievous sighs away
						from many. So they conducted her invisibly away again, but most of the
						small tapers remained in the room, and one of them accompanied each of us.
					-
