						feet - and the virgins were not sorry to see it - they quickly started up a
						civil dance, which I beheld with pleasure rather than taking part; for my
						mercurialists were so ready with their postures, as if they had long been
						of the trade. After a few dances our president came in again, and told us
						how the artists and students had offered themselves to their Royal
						Majesties, for their honour and pleasure, to act a merry comedy before
						their departure; and if we thought it good to be present at this, and to
						wait upon their Royal Majesties to the House of the Sun, it would be
						acceptable to them, and they would most graciously acknowledge it. Hereupon
