						"Here," he said, "lies buried Lady Venus, that beauty which has undone many
						a great man, both in fortune, honour, blessing and prosperity." After which
						he showed me a copper door on the pavement.
					-
				-
					Chapter 5: Section 3: Paragraph 5
				-
					-
