						Hereupon he turned the cock, and then the fountain no longer ran, and we
						had to remove it from the middle out of the way. After all things were
						carried off, he took leave, taking with him the casket with the glasses,
						and locked the door fast after him, so that we imagined nothing other but
						that we had been imprisoned in this Tower.
					-
